## Example for printing star pattern for pyramid 
```c

#include<stdio.h>
int
main ()
{
  int i, j;
  for (i = 1; i <= 5; i++)
    {

      for (j = i; j < 5; j++)
	{
	  printf (" ");
	}


      for (j = 1; j <= (2 * i - 1); j++)
	{
	  printf ("*");
	}


      printf ("\n");
    }

  return 0;
}
```
## Output:
```shell 
     *
    ***
   *****
  *******
 ********* 

``

